<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - Travel Adventure</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Ubuntu&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/aboutus.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>
    <div class="banner" id="bannerid">
      <div class="info">
        <h3>About us</h3>
        <p>
          "Embark on a journey with us, where every adventure is a story waiting
          to be written."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info2">
      <img
        src="/images/priscilla-du-preez-XkKCui44iM0-unsplash.jpg"
        id="hrteam_img"
        alt=""
      />
      <div class="hrteam_info">
        <h5>Welcome</h5>
        <p>
          TravelEase is a dynamic web application developed by a team of
          passionate individuals dedicated to simplifying the travel planning
          process. Our platform leverages cutting-edge AI technology to provide
          personalized recommendations and streamline every aspect of your
          journey. Whether you're a seasoned traveler or embarking on your first
          adventure, TravelEase is your trusted companion for creating
          unforgettable travel experiences. Join us as we redefine the way
          people explore the world.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info3">
      <div class="hrstory_info">
        <h5>Our Story</h5>
        <p>
          TravelEase was born as a passion project by a group of second-year
          students determined to simplify travel planning. Frustrated by
          existing platforms' lack of personalization, we set out to create a
          solution that would revolutionize the process.
        </p>
        <p>
          Despite challenges, we persevered, leveraging our diverse skills and
          boundless enthusiasm to develop a fully functional web application.
          Powered by AI technology, TravelEase offers personalized itineraries
          and real-time recommendations.
        </p>
        <p>
          As second-year students, TravelEase represents a significant milestone
          in our academic journey and a testament to our teamwork and
          determination. Join us as we continue to refine and expand TravelEase,
          empowering travelers to explore the world with confidence and ease.
        </p>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/images/carolina-marinelli-PkbyxvkGWcU-unsplash.jpg"
        id="hrstory_img"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="get_started">
      <p>Begin your journey here.</p>
      <a href="/itinerary"
        ><button id="get_started_btn" type="button">Get Started</button></a
      >
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
